# Prime Move Explorer

Interactive simulator of the Prime Move Operator.

The identical five-stage cycle (Split → Tension → Failed Merge → Scar → Decay) generates four growth pathways in real time from one seed:

- Spiral (φ convergence)
- Optimization
- Aggregation (fractal)
- Mixed

All panels run the same core rules with pathway-specific direction bias. Live scar-ratio tracking included.
